messages.messageBody:
Speaking of wands!!! I ordered Ethan a great wizard wand from the wand
shop. www.thewandshop.com They have a picture that your child can click on
and you get a custom wand made just for them! Ethan's had a dragon wisker
in his and came in a felt scabbard! Ooooh Ahhhhh! LOL The prices are
great, considering they are handmade. Anywhere from cheap to big bucks! :)

If nothing else, there's a lot of great info on the site if you have a young
wizard at heart. Fairy wands, wizard staves, cloaks, scabbards for the
wands, wizard lesson kits, quill and ink sets, the list is endless! Great
fun!

Jennifer
